lead_paragraph: Legia Warsaw have been fined 80,000 euros (68,894 pound) for crowd disturbances and their supporters banned from the club's next Champions League game at Borussia Dortmund on Nov. 22, UEFA said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Legia Warsaw Fans Banned for Dortmund Trip
